# A) Business Background



## Business Overview

RevoBank wants to increase the frequency of credit card usage by existing customers. The Performance Management (PM) team requested an analysis based on the last six months of transaction data to understand customer behavior and identify the most valuable user segments. The bank earns a profit from the Merchant Discount Rate (MDR) of 1.5% of the transaction value, but needs to consider potential losses from fraudulent transactions. A single customer can have multiple cards, so the analysis must consider a multi-account structure.

## Business Goal

Generate customer segmentation to increase MDR transactions and profits.


## Goal of Analysis

Clean Card data and User data



