Insight:
- In the segment (about to sleep), many customers have a fairly negative average usage, so you have to share valuable resources, recommend popular products / renewals at discounts, and reconnect with them.
- In the segment (recent customers) with the highest average usage of money, Revobank must be able to maintain and increase usage by providing on-boarding support, giving them early success, and starting to build relationships.
- The segment (customers needing attention) has a fairly large number of customers, so companies need to make limited-time offers, make recommendations based on past purchases, and reactivate them.

